{"id":115482,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/10/简讯：蒙牛就诽谤事件公开道歉/","date":"2010-10-22T17:52:03Z","modified":"2010-10-22T17:52:03Z","title":"简讯：蒙牛就诽谤事件公开道歉","content":"<div>\n<p>中国乳品巨头蒙牛就被曝光诽谤竞争对手一事公开道歉。</p>\n<p>蒙牛一名管理人员被控与公关公司合作诽谤伊利和圣元两家公司的产品可导致婴儿性早熟。</p>\n<p>有关诽谤在8月份令圣元公司陷入公关危机。</p>\n<p>蒙牛声称有关诽谤行为与公司无关，是涉案管理人员的个人行为。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/t5j_14EJbK-UXPzW4MnSu3JU62M/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/t5j_14EJbK-UXPzW4MnSu3JU62M/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/t5j_14EJbK-UXPzW4MnSu3JU62M/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/t5j_14EJbK-UXPzW4MnSu3JU62M/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=FpYGYRcmxzQ:rgyNQceI1Fc:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=FpYGYRcmxzQ:rgyNQceI1Fc:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=FpYGYRcmxzQ:rgyNQceI1Fc:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=FpYGYRcmxzQ:rgyNQceI1Fc:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=FpYGYRcmxzQ:rgyNQceI1Fc:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=FpYGYRcmxzQ:rgyNQceI1Fc:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/FpYGYRcmxzQ\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/201